Once Upon a Time in the West (2 disc edition) [1968]

Epic story of a mysterious stranger with a harmonica who joins forces with a
notorious desperado to protect a beautiful widow from a ruthless assassin
working for the railroad. 

Starring: Henry Fonda, Charles Bronson, Claudia Cardinale and Jason Robards 
Director: Sergio Leone
